132
00:07:55,220 --> 00:07:56,500
And be sure to let the police

133
00:07:56,780 --> 00:07:57,380
know

134
00:07:57,380 --> 00:07:58,540
how you harassed

135
00:07:58,540 --> 00:07:59,940
