136
00:08:01,380 --> 00:08:01,780
What...

137
00:08:02,340 --> 00:08:02,750
What...

138
00:08:02,820 --> 00:08:03,100
What...

139
00:08:03,150 --> 00:08:04,340
What do you want?

140
00:08:05,540 --> 00:08:07,540
Don't think showing me this video

141
00:08:07,540 --> 00:08:08,910
