156
00:08:31,430 --> 00:08:33,820
about your harassment
of our female artist

157
00:08:34,030 --> 00:08:35,750
and your unpaid balance.

158
00:08:44,780 --> 00:08:45,590
Li Munan,

159
00:08:46,100 --> 00:08:48,660
