167
00:09:11,030 --> 00:09:11,660
She also

168
00:09:11,750 --> 00:09:13,100
needs someone by her side at all times.

169
00:09:13,540 --> 00:09:14,660
Most importantly,

170
00:09:16,190 --> 00:09:18,780
